Ray F. DORNEY and Joe Pendleton, Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6920. Circuit "Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 15, 1932.

■ Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellee, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
